ging your word... so now im confused...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut \u0022one letter from the word\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nshard\u00A0\u2192 sharp, or hard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T13:13:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129408-kerbiloid/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129408\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129408-kerbiloid/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@kerbiloid\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0when this game started there was a rule that indicated you could change the word entirely, thus i changed your word out for a new one based upon my understanding of the rules at that time. It seems that the rules have since been altered. Which serves to underscore my confusion. \u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n081310262020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"probe137","CreatedById":207436,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-18T21:23:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhen\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-19T00:26:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBen\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Popestar","CreatedById":192906,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-19T00:37:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBean\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-19T05:42:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbeam\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-19T06:22:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nteam\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-19